text: , officially , is a district of Chiyoda, Tokyo, Japan. As of April 1, 2007, its population is 55. Its postal code is 101-0034. This district is located on the northeastern part of Chiyoda Ward. It borders Kanda-Higashimatsushitachō on the north, (across Shōwa-dōri Avenue) Iwamotochō on the east, Kanda- Konyachō on the south, and Kanda-Kitanorimonochō and Kanda-Konyachō on the west. It is a commercial district near the east exit of Kanda Station. Category:Districts of Chiyoda, Tokyo
